何が起こったのかよくわかんないよ！
but I'm not quite sure what happened!

987
00:59:39,248 --> 00:59:41,148
色がホントすごすぎて分からなくなってきたかも！
The colors are so intense I might be losing it!

988
00:59:41,248 --> 00:59:44,148
でも、まだもう一個すごく楽しみなことがあるんだよ！
But we still have one more very exciting thing to do!

989
00:59:44,248 --> 00:59:47,148
まだまだ楽しみがあるよ！
There's still more fun to come!

990
00:59:47,248 --> 00:59:49,148
わぁー！
Wow!

991
00:59:51,248 --> 00:59:54,148
何かなー？何かなー？
I wonder what it is? What is it?

992
00:59:57,148 --> 01:00:00,148
フワモコの1周年記念だよ！
It's FUWAMOCO's first anniversary!

993
01:00:01,529 --> 01:00:03,629
We were able to release our very first original song,

994
01:00:03,629 --> 01:00:06,129
"Wacha Wacha Party!" BAU BAU!

995
01:00:06,129 --> 01:00:10,229
And then for our second anniversary, we were able to release "Lifetime Showtime,"

996
01:00:10,229 --> 01:00:14,329
our original song that's been with us along this journey.

997
01:00:14,329 --> 01:00:16,929
A very special song.

998
01:00:16,929 --> 01:00:20,929
And you know, for FuwaMoco, singing and dancing

999
01:00:20,929 --> 01:00:23,529
is something that means so much to us.

1000
01:00:23,529 --> 01:00:25,229
Yeah, music!

1001
01:00:25,229 --> 01:00:28,729
And Ruffians, you might have heard

1002
01:00:28,729 --> 01:00:31,329
that you'd like to hear more from us too, right?

1003
01:00:31,329 --> 01:00:32,429
Yeah!

1004
01:00:32,429 --> 01:00:33,429
Yeah!

1005
01:00:33,429 --> 01:00:35,529
What do you think? Yeah!

1006
01:00:35,529 --> 01:00:38,029
Well, our announcement is...

1007
01:00:38,029 --> 01:00:42,029
Drumroll! OK, drumroll, yes!

1008
01:00:42,029 --> 01:00:46,229
Pupupupupupupupupupupupu...

1009
01:00:46,229 --> 01:00:50,329
DUN! A new original song!

1010
01:00:50,329 --> 01:00:54,329
新曲！新オリジナル曲！
A new song! A new original song!

1011
01:00:54,329 --> 01:00:57,229
And this song is extra special!

1012
01:00:57,229 --> 01:01:01,929
It's written by none other than the legendary

1013
01:01:01,929 --> 01:01:05,929
rock idol song composer Matsukuma Kenta-san,

1014
01:01:05,929 --> 01:01:10,029
who works with many famous idol groups we love,

1015
01:01:10,029 --> 01:01:14,129
also written music for the idol group that Kuro-chan produces,

1016
01:01:14,129 --> 01:01:16,829
MAMESHIBA NO TAIGUN-san!

1017
01:01:16,829 --> 01:01:19,729
But Ruffians, you might be a little bit surprised, OK?

1018
01:01:19,729 --> 01:01:22,529
So get ready.

1019
01:01:22,529 --> 01:01:25,529
Ruffians, with this song, we'd like to express

1020
01:01:25,529 --> 01:01:28,029
our deepest feelings as Demon Dogs.

1021
01:01:28,029 --> 01:01:31,529
DEMON'S RESIDENCE.

1022
01:01:46,029 --> 01:01:55,529
DEMON'S RESIDENCE
Lyrics: 海野水玉 Music: 松隈ケンタ Arrangement: SCRAMBLES
DEMON'S RESIDENCE
Lyrics: Mizutama Umino Music: Kenta Matsukuma Arrangement: SCRAMBLES

1023
01:01:55,929 --> 01:01:58,329
「相棒、どこへ行こうか」
"Partner, where shall we go?"

1024
01:01:58,329 --> 01:02:00,629
ネオンの脇を抜け
We slip past the neon lights

1025
01:02:00,629 --> 01:02:03,329
バブルガムがはじけたら
When the bubblegum pops

1026
01:02:03,329 --> 01:02:05,929
let's go

1027
01:02:05,929 --> 01:02:08,629
最低な夜を潜って
Diving through the worst of nights

1028
01:02:08,629 --> 01:02:11,129
僕らは群れをなす
We form our pack

1029
01:02:11,129 --> 01:02:13,829
「あの頃よりもマシだね」
"It's better than those days, isn't it?"

1030
01:02:13,829 --> 01:02:16,429
my way

1031
01:02:16,429 --> 01:02:19,029
「不完全なんです」
"We are incomplete"

1032
01:02:19,029 --> 01:02:21,629
首輪をつけた
Putting on our collars

1033
01:02:21,629 --> 01:02:24,329
良い子なんかじゃもう
We're no longer good girls

1034
01:02:24,329 --> 01:02:26,729
イ。ヤ。
No more.

1035
01:02:26,729 --> 01:02:29,829
Ah!! DEMON'S RESIDENCE 噛みついていけ
Ah!! DEMON'S RESIDENCE, go and bite

1036
01:02:29,829 --> 01:02:31,729
この街は檻のようで
This city is like a cage

1037
01:02:31,729 --> 01:02:34,329
気分はどうだい 泣いているのかい
How do you feel? Are you crying?

1038
01:02:34,329 --> 01:02:36,829
鎖をちぎって
Tear off the chains

1039
01:02:36,829 --> 01:02:39,329
叫んでいたいんだ stray dogs
I want to keep shouting, stray dogs

1040
01:02:39,329 --> 01:02:41,929
彼方へと飛ぶ鳥を
At the birds flying to the distance

1041
01:02:41,929 --> 01:02:44,429
見上げるだけかい それでいいのかい
Will you just look up? Is that enough for you?

1042
01:02:44,429 --> 01:02:47,029
燃えるなら ほら
If you're going to burn, look

1043
01:02:47,029 --> 01:02:52,529
青く
Burn blue

1044
01:02:57,529 --> 01:02:59,829
「説教なんかいらない」
"I don't need any lectures"

1045
01:02:59,829 --> 01:03:02,129
スプレー缶振って
Shake the spray can

1046
01:03:02,129 --> 01:03:04,829
イタズラ書きで彩る
Decorating with graffiti

1047
01:03:04,829 --> 01:03:07,429
runway
on the runway

1048
01:03:07,429 --> 01:03:09,829
愛情なんか coin toss
Love is just a coin toss

1049
01:03:09,829 --> 01:03:12,429
誰に bet するのか
Who are you betting on?

1050
01:03:12,429 --> 01:03:15,029
不確定要素ばかりね
Nothing but uncertain factors

1051
01:03:15,029 --> 01:03:17,629
lonely

1052
01:03:17,629 --> 01:03:20,229
二人でひとつと決めた
Decided we're two as one

1053
01:03:20,229 --> 01:03:22,829
あの日を忘れない
I won't forget that day

1054
01:03:22,829 --> 01:03:28,029
Ah!!

1055
01:03:28,029 --> 01:03:30,529
DEMON'S RESIDENCE 満天の空
DEMON'S RESIDENCE, the star-filled sky

1056
01:03:30,529 --> 01:03:33,029
あの星がひどく不快で
Those stars are so unpleasant

1057
01:03:33,029 --> 01:03:35,529
勝利はどうだい 味がするのかい
How's the victory? Does it have a taste?

1058
01:03:35,529 --> 01:03:38,229
鎖を噛んで
Bite the chains

1059
01:03:38,229 --> 01:03:40,829
唸っていたいんだ stray dogs
I want to keep growling, stray dogs

1060
01:03:40,829 --> 01:03:43,329
僕ら宇宙さえも撃ち落として
We'll shoot down even the universe

1061
01:03:43,329 --> 01:03:45,929
見下ろす奈落 ビルは輝く
Looking down at the abyss, the buildings shine

1062
01:03:45,929 --> 01:03:53,729
LOL Now I am free!!

1063
01:04:03,829 --> 01:04:14,129
Woah woah woah...

1064
01:04:14,129 --> 01:04:19,229
孤独を分け合い食べた
We shared and ate our loneliness

1065
01:04:19,229 --> 01:04:24,429
あの日を忘れない
I won't forget that day

1066
01:04:24,429 --> 01:04:26,929
嗚呼 夜を睨んだ stray dogs そうだ
Ah, staring into the night, stray dogs, that's right

1067
01:04:26,929 --> 01:04:29,429
怪物（モンスター）は世界のほうさ
The monsters are the world itself

1068
01:04:29,429 --> 01:04:32,029
抜け出せるのかい 足は動くかい
Can you escape? Can your legs move?

1069
01:04:32,029 --> 01:04:34,529
走るなら今
If you're going to run, now's the time

1070
01:04:34,529 --> 01:04:37,029
DEMON'S RESIDENCE stray dogs 僕ら
DEMON'S RESIDENCE, stray dogs, we

1071
01:04:37,029 --> 01:04:39,629
この街を駆けて行け
Will run through this city

1072
01:04:39,629 --> 01:04:42,229
地獄の果てに 何が見えるかい
At the end of hell, what will you see?

1073
01:04:42,229 --> 01:04:44,729
鎖をちぎって
Tear off the chains

1074
01:04:44,729 --> 01:04:47,229
叫んでいたいんだ stray dogs 僕ら
I want to keep shouting, stray dogs, we

1075
01:04:47,229 --> 01:04:49,829
この街は檻のようで
This city is like a cage

1076
01:04:49,829 --> 01:04:52,429
君ならどうだい 共に駆けるかい？
How about you? Will you run with us?

1077
01:04:52,429 --> 01:04:54,929
夜明けが合図だ
Dawn is the signal

1078
01:04:54,929 --> 01:05:00,029
行こう
Let's go

1079
