side by side

1096
01:05:51,584 --> 01:05:52,584
Bau bau!

1097
01:05:52,784 --> 01:05:56,884
Thank you for always being here for us, Ruffians!

1098
01:05:57,684 --> 01:06:00,884
Please listen to "side by side"!

1099
01:06:04,784 --> 01:06:08,684
Finally we made it through but not without some tears

1100
01:06:12,084 --> 01:06:16,184
With the help of friends so true we faced all of our fears

1101
01:06:19,384 --> 01:06:23,384
Now we're here to celebrate all that we have done

1102
01:06:26,584 --> 01:06:30,584
I can feel it's more than just a game of fate

1103
01:06:30,684 --> 01:06:33,084
'cause our stories have just begun

1104
01:06:35,184 --> 01:06:38,084
Hand in hand we're not waiting on tomorrow

1105
01:06:38,884 --> 01:06:42,384
From now on it's the heart that we will follow

1106
01:06:42,884 --> 01:06:46,384
We'll move on past the heartbreak and the sorrow if you

1107
01:06:46,684 --> 01:06:49,984
Stay by my side

1108
01:06:50,784 --> 01:06:54,184
Dancing harmonies feeding the music

1109
01:06:54,284 --> 01:06:57,284
as we come alive, and sparks ignite

1110
01:06:58,184 --> 01:07:01,684
We're making memories everyday underneath

1111
01:07:01,784 --> 01:07:05,184
the summer sky and through the night

1112
01:07:06,084 --> 01:07:09,384
We're singing melodies every time we hear music

1113
01:07:09,484 --> 01:07:12,884
from inside as hearts collide

1114
01:07:13,684 --> 01:07:17,084
Bringing out the best in each other

1115
01:07:17,184 --> 01:07:20,984
now we're feeling free like we're meant to be

1116
01:07:21,784 --> 01:07:25,284
Even though, there's been rough times when nobody wanted us,

1117
01:07:25,384 --> 01:07:28,084
We kept going, and we kept dreaming!

1118
01:07:28,984 --> 01:07:30,984
Now we're here, we're not alone anymore,

1119
01:07:31,084 --> 01:07:33,984
Ruffians are together, we have smiles to protect!

1120
01:07:34,084 --> 01:07:35,784
Come on, let's go!

1121
01:07:36,584 --> 01:07:39,984
Dancing harmonies feeding the music

1122
01:07:40,084 --> 01:07:43,084
as we come alive, and sparks ignite

1123
