Bringing out the best in each other

1128
01:08:02,984 --> 01:08:06,684
now we're feeling free like we're meant to be

1129
01:08:07,484 --> 01:08:14,784
Nya nya nya nya...

1130
01:08:14,884 --> 01:08:22,184
Nya nya nya nya...

1131
01:08:22,284 --> 01:08:29,884
Nya nya nya nya...

1132
01:08:29,984 --> 01:08:37,984
Nya nya nya nya...

1133
01:08:38,984 --> 01:08:39,984
Bau bau!

1134
01:08:45,784 --> 01:08:48,884
Thank you for the encore, Ruffians!

1135
01:08:48,984 --> 01:08:52,884
That was "side by side"! Bau bau!

1136
01:08:53,684 --> 01:08:58,084
We're really happy to perform "side by side" for the first time live today!

1137
01:08:58,184 --> 01:09:01,684
Yeah! 初披露できてとっても嬉しいです！
Yeah! I'm so happy we got to perform it for the first time!

1138
01:09:01,784 --> 01:09:05,484
"side by side" is a song made by Alobahn-san, but also between FuwaMoco!

1139
01:09:05,584 --> 01:09:08,984
Yeah, and us!

1140
01:09:09,084 --> 01:09:13,384
I know, we know it's a song that you love a lot,

1141
01:09:13,484 --> 01:09:20,084
but we also do because it's very special to us since it's the ending theme for a visual novel that we care about!

1142
01:09:20,184 --> 01:09:20,984
Nekopara!

1143
01:09:21,084 --> 01:09:24,084
Nekopara! Bau bau!

1144
01:09:24,184 --> 01:09:31,584
And with this song, our dream of singing the opening or ending theme for a visual novel came true!

1145
01:09:31,684 --> 01:09:37,684
Yeah! そう、この曲でフワモコの夢、美少女ゲームの主題歌を歌うことが叶いました！
Yeah! That's right, with this song, FuwaMoco's dream of singing a bishojo game theme song has come true!

1146
01:09:37,784 --> 01:09:41,984
Yeah, it came true! Thank you!

1147
01:09:42,084 --> 01:09:42,784
Thank you!

1148
01:09:42,884 --> 01:09:45,284
ありがとう！
Thank you!

1149
01:09:45,384 --> 01:09:49,884
And thank you so much for joining us for our special day again this year!

1150
01:09:49,984 --> 01:09:51,384
It's been a dream with you!

1151
01:09:51,484 --> 01:09:54,884
And you know, it's all because of you that we're able to be here

1152
01:09:54,984 --> 01:09:58,084
and do all the amazing things that we do, so thank you!

1153
01:09:58,184 --> 01:09:59,084
Thank you!

1154
01:10:00,965 --> 01:10:02,265
This next song...

1155
01:10:02,265 --> 01:10:04,065
...is our last song!

1156
01:10:04,465 --> 01:10:08,365
But like all of them, it's a very special one.

1157
01:10:08,965 --> 01:10:10,965
You know FUWAMOCO...

1158
01:10:10,965 --> 01:10:12,765
...is Demon Guard Dogs!

1159
01:10:12,765 --> 01:10:15,465
We're here to protect your smile, right?

1160
01:10:15,465 --> 01:10:17,765
We'll continue to do that.

1161
01:10:17,765 --> 01:10:18,465
Protect your smile!

1162
01:10:18,465 --> 01:10:19,165
Yeah!

1163
01:10:19,165 --> 01:10:21,065
Do our best as idols!

1164
01:10:21,065 --> 01:10:24,965
And just as our fluffy and fuzzy souls, too.

1165
01:10:24,965 --> 01:10:28,965
We'll continue to be here for
thousands and thousands of demon dog years.

1166
01:10:28,965 --> 01:10:33,365
All while remembering that, you know,
every day isn't given.

1167
01:10:33,765 --> 01:10:34,965
Yeah!

1168
01:10:34,965 --> 01:10:37,365
We don't take anything for granted.

1169
01:10:37,365 --> 01:10:42,165
And you know, when you're down,
we hope that you'll remember...

1170
01:10:42,165 --> 01:10:43,965
...that we're always here cheering you on, okay?

1171
01:10:43,965 --> 01:10:45,965
We'll cheer you on, Ruffians!

1172
01:10:46,465 --> 01:10:50,965
So please listen closely to the lyrics
of our last song for today.

1173
01:11:04,465 --> 01:11:07,465
明日も　明後日も
Tomorrow, and the day after too,

1174
01:11:07,765 --> 01:11:12,965
あなたが笑ってますように　ずっと
I hope you'll keep on smiling forever.

1175
01:11:14,165 --> 01:11:17,765
Lala...

1176
01:11:18,465 --> 01:11:21,965
Thank you so much Ruffians for
spending our birthday with us today!

1177
01:11:22,465 --> 01:11:25,165
Please think of this song whenever things are rough...

1178
01:11:25,165 --> 01:11:28,465
...and know we'll be here!

1179
01:11:28,465 --> 01:11:30,465
This last song is for you, Wishful☆Garnet!

1180
01:11:32,165 --> 01:11:34,765
過去を振り返ると
When I look back at the past,

1181
01:11:34,765 --> 01:11:39,165
思い出すガーネットの空
I remember the Garnet sky.

1182
01:11:40,965 --> 01:11:44,465
溢れてく　光
The light overflows.

1183
01:11:45,165 --> 01:11:49,465
この瞳に映し出されたあの日は
That day reflected in these eyes

1184
01:11:49,465 --> 01:11:54,965
美しく　揺れる
sways beautifully.

1185
01:11:55,465 --> 01:11:57,465
What do you think?

1186
01:11:57,765 --> 01:12:01,965
赤く滲んだ空に
In the sky tinged with red,

1187
01:12:02,465 --> 01:12:09,465
願いました　どうかこの願い　届けてください
I made a wish. Please, let this wish reach you.

1188
01:12:10,465 --> 01:12:12,765
明日も　明後日も
Tomorrow, and the day after too,

1189
01:12:12,765 --> 01:12:16,965
あなたが笑ってますように
I hope you'll keep on smiling.

1190
01:12:16,965 --> 01:12:22,965
離れ離れになっても　前を向けますように
Even if we are far apart, I hope you can look forward.

1191
01:12:23,165 --> 01:12:28,465
あなたを縛る鎖を　わたしが壊してあげる
The chains that bind you, I will break them for you.

1192
01:12:29,465 --> 01:12:34,165
もう負けないで進むこと　いつでもそばにいるから
Keep moving forward without losing,
because I'll always be by your side.

1193
01:12:49,765 --> 01:12:56,465
落ち込んだり自信を無くした時だって
Even when I felt down or lost my confidence,

1194
01:12:56,965 --> 01:13:00,965
目の前にいてくれる
you were right there in front of me.

1195
01:13:00,965 --> 01:13:08,465
あなたの笑顔に何度となく　救われた
I've been saved by your smile time and time again.

1196
01:13:09,465 --> 01:13:11,465
だから
That's why,

1197
01:13:11,465 --> 01:13:13,465
So I love you

1198
01:13:13,465 --> 01:13:19,965
挫けそうになったら　手を伸ばして
If you feel like giving up, just reach out your hand.

1199
01:13:20,165 --> 01:13:26,765
まだ知らない明日　一緒に見つけよう
Let's find the unknown tomorrow together.

1200
01:13:27,465 --> 01:13:32,965
明日も　明後日も　あなたを照らしていたい
Tomorrow, and the day after too, I want to keep shining on you.

1201
01:13:33,165 --> 01:13:38,465
泣きそうになった時は　こっち向いてほしい
When you feel like crying, please look my way.

